    "# 1.5 函数类型\n",
    "\n",
    "> 目标：掌握函数的类型注解写法"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 函数类型注解\n",
    "\n",
    "```typescript\n",
    "// 普通函数\n",
    "function add(a: number, b: number): number {\n",
    "  return a + b;\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "// 箭头函数\n",
    "const multiply = (a: number, b: number): number => a * b;\n",
    "\n",
    "// 可选参数（用 ? 标记）\n",
    "function greet(name: string, greeting?: string): string {\n",
    "  return `${greeting || \"Hello\"}, ${name}!`;\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "// 默认参数\n",
    "function log(message: string, level: string = \"info\"): void {\n",
    "  console.log(`[${level}] ${message}`);\n",
    "}\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "// 函数示例\n",
    "function normalizeChannelId(kind: string, id: string): string {\n",
    "  return `${kind}:${id}`.toLowerCase();\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "// 可选参数\n",
    "function buildTarget(kind: string, id: string, prefix?: string): string {\n",
    "  const normalized = normalizeChannelId(kind, id);\n",
    "  return prefix ? `${prefix}:${normalized}` : normalized;\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "console.log(normalizeChannelId(\"user\", \"123\"));\n",
    "console.log(buildTarget(\"channel\", \"general\"));\n",
    "console.log(buildTarget(\"channel\", \"general\", \"telegram\"));\n",
    "\n",
    "undefined;"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 项目中的例子\n",
    "\n",
    "### 来自 src/channels/targets.ts\n",
    "\n",
    "```typescript\n",
    "export function normalizeTargetId(\n",
    "  kind: MessagingTargetKind, \n",
    "  id: string\n",
    "): string {\n",
    "  return `${kind}:${id}`.toLowerCase();\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "export function buildMessagingTarget(\n",
    "  kind: MessagingTargetKind,\n",
    "  id: string,\n",
    "  raw: string,\n",
    "): MessagingTarget {\n",
    "  return {\n",
    "    kind,\n",
    "    id,\n",
    "    raw,\n",
    "    normalized: normalizeTargetId(kind, id),\n",
    "  };\n",
    "}\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 函数类型作为类型\n",
    "\n    "```typescript\n",
    "// 定义函数类型\n",
    "type SendMessage = (target: string, content: string) => Promise<void>;\n",
    "\n",
    "// 使用函数类型\n",
    "const sendTelegram: SendMessage = async (target, content) => {\n",
    "  // 实现...\n",
    "};\n",
    "\n",
    "const sendDiscord: SendMessage = async (target, content) => {\n",
    "  // 实现...\n",
    "};\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "这种写法在 OpenClaw 的 `src/cli/deps.ts` 中有使用。"
   ]
  },
